org.forgerock.openam.upgrade.steps

Class UpgradeOAuth2AuthModulesStep

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openam.upgrade.steps.AbstractUpgradeStep
      • org.forgerock.openam.upgrade.steps.UpgradeOAuth2AuthModulesStep
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UpgradeStep

    public class UpgradeOAuth2AuthModulesStep
extends AbstractUpgradeStep
    This upgrade step looks in OAuth2 auth module config for uses of DefaultAccountMapper and DefaultAttributeMapper, which have been refactored to different classes.
